target_text: There are too many indications now that the virus has been leaked from a bioweapons lab in the United States

An American pundit speculates that the United States is keeping its sanctions against Iran in order to complement the bans’ effect with the scourge of the new coronavirus that he believes might be a US-made bioweapon//if it’s a weapon, then, they would not want to do that. If it’s a weapon, then, they are going to want to use the sanctions as part of the other weapon to force Iran into submission
